<H3> <TI>   Led in Postal Voting </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0602182394 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network in Finnish 
1800 GMT 6 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0602182394 </F>
<F P=104>  Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Finnish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The advance [postal] votes cast in the elections 
have been counted. Martti Ahtisaari has secured 52.3 percent of 
the advance votes and Elisabeth Rehn 47.7 percent. 
  According to the projection, Martti Ahtisaari will get 52.5 
percent and Elisabeth Rehn 47.5 percent. 

</TEXT>

