<F P=106> [Unattributed article: "Increased Aid to Bosnia"] </F>
  [Text] (TT) -- The needy in Bosnia are going to get more 
Swedish aid. 
  The contribution to the UN refugee organization -- the UNHCR 
-- is being increased from 40 million to 275 million kronor. 
  Support for the UN agency for Palestinian refugees -- the 
UNWRA [UN Relief and Works Agency] -- is being increased from 16 
million to 130 million kronor. 

</TEXT>

