<F P=106> [Unattributed article: "UN Will Not Receive Less Support"] </F>
  [Text] (TT) -- The Swedish threat to reduce support for UN 
agencies will not be carried out following promised reforms. 
  UNICEF, the UN children's fund, will receive the same amount 
as before -- 350 million kronor -- and the UNDP [UN Development 
Program] will get 146 million kronor, which is 10 million kronor 
more than in the last fiscal year. 

