<F P=100> GREECE </F>
<H3> <TI>   Coast Guard Confiscates 60 Kgs of Cocaine </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0402164094 Athens ATHENS NEWS in English 4 Feb 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> NC0402164094 </F>
<F P=104>  Athens ATHENS NEWS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Greece's Coast Guard yesterday made the largest ever 
cocaine seizure in Greek history when it discovered 60 kgs of 
the drug hidden aboard a ship, the Ministry of Merchant Marine 
said last night. The cocaine, in paste form, was found in the 
engine exhausts of the 10,736 ton Panamanian-flagged Kinaros V. 
after it went into a dry dock near Athens for repairs. The 
vessel, a refrigerator ship, had been sitting in port for nearly 
eight months after returning from a trip to Colombia. 

</TEXT>

