<H3> <TI>   Cabinet Approves 16 Oct Bundestag Election Date </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0902120394 Berlin N-TV in German 1100 GMT 9 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0902120394 </F>
<F P=104>  Berlin N-TV </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The German Cabinet has approved a new law on the 
introduction of highway tolls. According to the law, highway 
charges will be payable for trucks weighing more than 12 tonnes 
from 1995 onwards. 
  The cabinet also finally approved 16 October as the date for 
this year's Bundestag elections. Leading coalition and Social 
Democratic Party politicians had earlier expressed themselves in 
favor of this date. 

</TEXT>

